55:30.000 --> 55:30.867
It manages to slide into people's ears.

55:31.466 --> 55:35.300
It slips inside their brains.

55:35.967 --> 55:40.000
Then it swells and it stuns.

55:46.367 --> 55:48.667
It comes out of the mouth...

